headline: Corteva, Inc.: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: INDIANAPOLIS (AP) — Corteva, Inc. CTVA) on Tuesday reported a loss of $552 million in its fourth quarter. The Indianapolis-based company said it had a loss of 82 cents per share.

headline: Strong 2H and Full Year 2025 Results Driven by Leading Technology, Disciplined Execution
